{
  "id": "dating-after-breakup-with-child-involved",
  "title": "Dating After Breakup (With Child Involved)",
  "tags": ["post-breakup", "parenting", "dating", "emotional-recovery"],
  "version": "1.3.0",
  "meters": ["trust", "tension", "childStress"],
  "acts": [
    {
      "id": "act1",
      "title": "The First Weekend Without the Child",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "a1s1",
          "text": "The toys are still on the couch. It’s Friday evening and the silence feels heavier than expected.",
          "tone": "reflective · gentle melancholy",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a1s1c1",
              "text": "I’ll clean up and make some dinner — I need to get back into routine.",
              "tone": "mature · self-care",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a1s2"
            },
            {
              "id": "a1s1c2",
              "text": "I’ll text my friend to go out — I need to distract myself.",
              "tone": "impulsive · escapist",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a1s2"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a1s2",
          "text": "Your friend replies quickly: “We’re at the new bar downtown — come join us!” You hesitate.",
          "tone": "ambivalent · tentative",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a1s2c1",
              "text": "I’ll go. Maybe a bit of socializing will help.",
              "tone": "open · exploratory",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a1s3"
            },
            {
              "id": "a1s2c2",
              "text": "No, I think I’ll stay home. This feels forced.",
              "tone": "self-protective · grounded",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a1s3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a1s3",
          "text": "Just as you settle in, your phone lights up — a message from your ex: “Did you pack the extra pajamas? She says she can’t find them.”",
          "tone": "practical · co-parenting micro-stress",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a1s3c1",
              "text": "Yes, they’re in the blue bag. Try checking the side pocket.",
              "tone": "calm · cooperative",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a1s4"
            },
            {
              "id": "a1s3c2",
              "text": "You could’ve checked before texting me.",
              "tone": "frustrated · defensive",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 1 }
              ],
              "next": "a1s4"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a1s4",
          "text": "Lying in bed, you scroll through social media. Everyone seems to be in couples or on trips.",
          "tone": "lonely · self-comparison",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a1s4c1",
              "text": "I’ll log off — this isn’t helping.",
              "tone": "self-aware · boundary-setting",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a1end"
            },
            {
              "id": "a1s4c2",
              "text": "Maybe I’ll re-download the dating app… just to look.",
              "tone": "curious · slightly anxious",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a1end"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a1end",
          "text": "You lie awake for a moment, thinking about how strange this new life feels — quieter, but full of possibilities.",
          "tone": "quiet · open-ended",
          "summary": {
            "highTrust": "You’ve kept your composure and handled the weekend with maturity — you’re ready to move forward.",
            "highTension": "The silence stings and emotions flicker. There’s healing to do, but you’re learning what you need.",
            "highChildStress": "Even when apart, your thoughts circle back to your child — guilt mixes with care."
          },
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a1endc1",
              "text": "Continue to Act 2.",
              "tone": "gentle · hopeful",
              "next": "act2s1"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "act2",
      "title": "The Swipe of Possibility",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "act2s1",
          "text": "Saturday morning. Sunlight spills across your phone. The dating app icon is still there — waiting. You hesitate before tapping it.",
          "tone": "tentative · curious",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a2s1c1",
              "text": "I’ll open it. Just curious who’s out there.",
              "tone": "open · cautious",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a2s2"
            },
            {
              "id": "a2s1c2",
              "text": "No, not yet. I don’t want to rush into anything.",
              "tone": "measured · patient",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a2s2"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a2s2",
          "text": "You scroll through a few profiles — smiles, bios, small talk hooks. It’s both exciting and exhausting.",
          "tone": "ambivalent · overstimulated",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a2s2c1",
              "text": "Swipe right on someone interesting — what’s the harm?",
              "tone": "playful · testing waters",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a2s3"
            },
            {
              "id": "a2s2c2",
              "text": "Close the app. This doesn’t feel like me right now.",
              "tone": "self-preserving · clear boundary",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a2s3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a2s3",
          "text": "Just then, your child’s photo pops up on your lock screen — a reminder from the shared album with your ex.",
          "tone": "tender · grounding",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a2s3c1",
              "text": "Smile softly — they look happy. That’s what matters.",
              "tone": "warm · reassured",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a2s4"
            },
            {
              "id": "a2s3c2",
              "text": "Feel a sting of guilt — maybe this isn’t the time to date.",
              "tone": "guilty · conflicted",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 1 }
              ],
              "next": "a2s4"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a2s4",
          "text": "Later that day, your friend texts again: “So, any cute matches yet?” You laugh — maybe, maybe not.",
          "tone": "light · slightly teasing",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a2s4c1",
              "text": "Be honest: 'I tried it, but it felt weird.'",
              "tone": "honest · self-aware",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a2end"
            },
            {
              "id": "a2s4c2",
              "text": "Joke: 'Already planning the wedding.'",
              "tone": "humorous · deflecting",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a2end"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a2end",
          "text": "As the weekend closes, you realize this was the first time you let yourself think about your own happiness — not just responsibilities.",
          "tone": "soft · contemplative",
          "summary": {
            "highTrust": "You’ve taken a healthy step forward. There’s space now for self-kindness and new beginnings.",
            "highTension": "Your emotions still wrestle between guilt and curiosity, but at least you’re honest with yourself.",
            "highChildStress": "Even while exploring new ground, your child stays at the heart of every decision."
          },
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a2endc1",
              "text": "Continue to Act 3.",
              "tone": "hopeful · steady",
              "next": "a3s1"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "act3",
      "title": "First Real Connection",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "a3s1",
          "text": "A new notification glows on your phone: “Hey, you seem interesting :)” — your first match, or maybe just the universe testing you.",
          "tone": "tentative · surprised · gentle humor",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a3s1c1",
              "text": "Hi! Thanks — I wasn’t sure I’d even try this.",
              "tone": "open · humble · vulnerable optimism",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a3s2"
            },
            {
              "id": "a3s1c2",
              "text": "Maybe another time.",
              "tone": "reserved · quiet · self-protective",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a3s2"
            },
            {
              "id": "a3s1c3",
              "text": "Careful, I’m still under emotional construction 🚧.",
              "tone": "playful · self-ironic · humor masking caution",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a3s2"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a3s2",
          "text": "The glow of the screen fades; your reflection stares back. For the first time in months, you ask yourself what you actually want.",
          "tone": "introspective · slow pacing · gentle internal monologue",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a3s2c1",
              "text": "I want companionship, not distraction.",
              "tone": "mature · centred · soft conviction",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a3s3"
            },
            {
              "id": "a3s2c2",
              "text": "I just miss being wanted.",
              "tone": "melancholic · self-aware · aching honesty",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a3s3"
            },
            {
              "id": "a3s2c3",
              "text": "Maybe I’m doing okay — just figuring things out.",
              "tone": "balanced · accepting · calm exhale",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a3s3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a3s3",
          "text": "Your child calls from your ex’s phone: “Daddy/Mommy, can we go to the park tomorrow?” The sound of their voice melts any remaining tension.",
          "tone": "warm · tender · grounding",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a3s3c1",
              "text": "Of course! I missed you.",
              "tone": "loving · gentle · immediate warmth",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a3end"
            },
            {
              "id": "a3s3c2",
              "text": "We’ll see, I have things to do.",
              "tone": "tired · detached · subtle guilt undertone",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 1 }
              ],
              "next": "a3end"
            },
            {
              "id": "a3s3c3",
              "text": "I’d love that — maybe we can bring the kite.",
              "tone": "joyful · playful · re-energized",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a3end"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a3end",
          "text": "Later, as the sky turns amber, you realize balance isn’t about forgetting the past — it’s about making space for what’s next.",
          "tone": "meditative · lightly hopeful · closure vibe",
          "summary": {
            "highTrust": "You’re beginning to rebuild — carefully, but genuinely.",
            "highTension": "The tug-of-war between guilt and desire still lingers, yet awareness is progress.",
            "highChildStress": "Your love for your child keeps grounding you — every step forward includes them."
          },
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a3endc1",
              "text": "Continue to Act 4.",
              "tone": "calm · optimistic",
              "next": "act4"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "act4",
      "title": "The First Date Dilemma",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "a4s1",
          "text": "Late afternoon. You check the mirror one last time. It’s your first real date since the breakup — excitement and nerves tangle together.",
          "tone": "anticipatory · hopeful · slightly anxious",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a4s1c1",
              "text": "Confirm pickup logistics with your ex before you leave.",
              "tone": "responsible · proactive",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s2"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s1c2",
              "text": "Skip logistics — it’ll be fine.",
              "tone": "avoidant · optimistic",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s2"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s1c3",
              "text": "Cancel the date — you’re not ready.",
              "tone": "self-protective · low energy",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4end"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a4s2",
          "text": "Phone in hand. A message field to your ex blinks: pickup tomorrow at 10:00? You can set the tone now.",
          "tone": "practical · boundary-setting opportunity",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a4s2c1",
              "text": "Be clear and kind: 'Pickup at 10:00 at the park entrance, I’ll confirm in the morning.'",
              "tone": "calm · collaborative",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s3"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s2c2",
              "text": "Keep it vague: 'I’ll text you tomorrow.'",
              "tone": "noncommittal · hedging",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s3"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s2c3",
              "text": "Sound irritated: 'Just be ready whenever, okay?'",
              "tone": "irritable · controlling",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 1 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a4s3",
          "text": "At the café. Your date smiles, easy conversation bubbling. They ask about your weekend. The parenting question hangs in the air.",
          "tone": "warm · curious · vulnerable",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a4s3c1",
              "text": "Be upfront about being a parent and what that means for your time.",
              "tone": "honest · grounded",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s4"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s3c2",
              "text": "Keep it light — mention your child briefly, then pivot to hobbies.",
              "tone": "balanced · socially attuned",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s4"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s3c3",
              "text": "Overshare about your ex and the breakup details.",
              "tone": "nervous · overdisclosing",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4s4"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a4s4",
          "text": "Later, the date suggests a spontaneous late movie. It would push past your usual wind-down before pickup.",
          "tone": "temptation · boundary test",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a4s4c1",
              "text": "Set a clear boundary: 'I’d love to, but I need rest to be present tomorrow.'",
              "tone": "assertive · caring · self-respect",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": -1 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": -1 }
              ],
              "next": "a4end"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s4c2",
              "text": "Compromise: 'Let’s grab a short walk instead.'",
              "tone": "creative · flexible",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": 1 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 0 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 0 }
              ],
              "next": "a4end"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4s4c3",
              "text": "Ignore the boundary and go anyway.",
              "tone": "impulsive · avoidant",
              "effects": [
                { "meter": "trust", "delta": -2 },
                { "meter": "tension", "delta": 2 },
                { "meter": "childStress", "delta": 1 }
              ],
              "next": "a4end"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "a4end",
          "text": "Home again. Shoes by the door, quiet in the hall. You replay the night — the small risks, the small wins — and notice you’re breathing easier.",
          "tone": "settled · gently optimistic",
          "summary": {
            "highTrust": "Your boundaries and honesty created space for something real.",
            "highTension": "The pull between desire and duty is still loud, but you named it — that matters.",
            "highChildStress": "You steered the night with your child in mind. That care is your compass."
          },
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "a4endc1",
              "text": "Continue to Act 5.",
              "tone": "confident · forward-looking",
              "next": "act5"
            },
            {
              "id": "a4endc2",
              "text": "Pause here (return to menu).",
              "tone": "reflective · contained",
              "next": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
